between India and Pakistan over Kashmir.
</P>
<P>
   ''If you look at how well the Indians, the Pakistanis and the
Bangladeshis who have come to America have done -- the extraordinary
percentage of them who are involved in high-tech economy
professions -- it is tragic to think what this conflict has done to
hold back the people.''
</P>
<P>
   ------
</P>
