hybrid vehicle design based on DaimlerChrysler cargo vans. The vans
will be powered by Electric Fuel's batteries as the main energy
storage.
</P>
<P>
   The organizers - including the German Federal Science Ministry -
seek to develop high-performance, clean electric transportation.
</P>
<P>
   Electric Fuel has corporate and sales offices in New Jersey.
</P>
<P>
   On the Net: www.electric-fuel.com
