   On the Net:
</P>
<P>
   Clinton remarks: 
http://www.whitehouse.gov/library/hot--releases/September--15--2000--1.h
tml
</P>
<P>
   Lee supporters: http://www.wenholee.org
</P>
<P>
   Reno statement on Lee's guilty plea:
http://www.usdoj.gov/opa/pr/2000/September/537ag.htm
</P>
</TEXT>
