   Mrs. Lieberman visited her mother Thursday and early Friday
before returning to Washington with her husband.
</P>
<P>
   Mrs. Freilich, who is in her early 80s, and her late husband,
Samuel, came to the United States with Hadassah from Czechoslovakia
in the early 1950s after having survived Nazi concentration camps.
Samuel Freilich died in 1993.
